

   #  2 Types
      +  Reliable Receiver
         -  Sends acknowledgement to the Source when the data has been received and stored
            in spark with Replication  
         -  Breadcrumb
            .  Sources like Kafka & Flume has facility receive acknowledgement for the transferred
               data ; which helps to create Reliable Receiver
      +  Unreliable receiver
         -  Do not send acknowledgement to the Source
         

http://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/streaming-programming-guide.html#receiver-reliability         
                     
            